{"tid":784152,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[奧匈捷]10日遊行程","createTime":"2018-08-18T06:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T11:43:28.000Z","uid":200050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"49fe31383283cb427c59d7b14b4f3cc58f4d0449","tid":784152,"uid":200050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:50:01.000Z","msg":"黎緊11日會去布拉格十日左右, plan左行程, 大家比下意見,討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該會由布拉格入, 布達佩斯走, 一到布拉格應該8:XX am<br />\nDay 1-2 布拉格, 老城區同城堡區各玩一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDay 3 一早由布拉格搭Student Agency去CK小鎮, 之後都係去下彩色塔個d景點<br />\nDay 4 一早搭CK Shuttle去Hallstatt, 之後同圍行下,  去下Postcard位影相<br />\nDay 5 又係一早火車去Salzburg, 到埗後去下莫札特故居,老城購物街個d景點咁<br />\nDay 6 諗緊留多日係Salzburg好定下午就搭OBB去Vienna好,, 好多人話可以去國王湖, 但之前已經去過啦, 今次應該唔去啦, 但唔知仲有邊度順路去,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDay 7-8 Vienna, plan左會去教堂丫, 市集,奧地利國會大廈, 百水屋個d咁<br />\nDay 8-10 Budapest, 都係去下D景點, 塞錢尼鏈橋, 漁夫堡, 塞切尼溫泉浴場個d, <br />\n<br />\n其實每個地方都搭差唔多3個鐘車程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 一日一地方會唔會好chur,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但d小鎮又行一日已經行曬,同埋d交通好多都係得朝早車, 好似布拉格去CK小鎮咁, 得09:00或是10:00揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nching比d意見~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18807c51db85c15f25e2c7e9dc828e79e0114eae","tid":784152,"uid":200050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a547e1ea282d071624655164a12be694543834","tid":784152,"uid":10385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:43:05.000Z","msg":"Salzburg個人黎講覺得幾悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g